fields.name: PANTRY GLASS BIDDING
fields.details:
Perfect connections between basket and door.
Soft close feature ensures effortless functioning.
In-built slide-out mechanism for easy accessibility.
Clear classification, more storage space, convenient and smooth operation.
Tandem Pantry Unit bottom slider is tested with 50,000 cycle.
This kitchen pantry unit is ideal for pantry storage of 450mm & 600mm wide cabinets.
Color – black / Glass.
